OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782301688
OL,3,CDrivers risk #110 fines for trying to
OL,4,Ckeep cool in stationary cars with air
OL,5,Ccon
OL,7,FBut some local authorities use their
OL,8,Fpowers to impose larger fines.
OL,10,FIslington Council said its enforcement
OL,11,Fofficers issue #110 fines to people
OL,12,Fwho refuse to switch off an idling
OL,13,Fengine after being asked.
OL,15,FRAC senior policy officer Rod Dennis
OL,16,Fsaid: "Air conditioning is a
OL,17,Fgamechanger in modern vehicles, making
OL,18,Fotherwise uncomfortable journeys by
OL,19,Froad a genuinely pleasant experience.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
