OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782301688
OL,3,CDrivers risk #110 fines for trying to
OL,4,Ckeep cool in stationary cars with air
OL,5,Ccon
OL,7,F"We even advise those driving vehicles
OL,8,Fwithout air-con to consider delaying
OL,9,Fany non-essential trips this week
OL,10,Funtil the heatwave passes.
OL,12,F"But while we're all desperate to stay
OL,13,Fcool, just sitting in the car with the
OL,14,Fengine and air-conditioning running
OL,15,Fand going nowhere isn't advisable.
OL,17,F"Due to the air pollution this causes,
OL,18,Fyou risk a fine from a police or civil
OL,19,Fenforcement officer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
