CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782301688
OL,3,CDrivers risk #110 fines for trying to
OL,4,Ckeep cool in stationary cars with air
OL,5,Ccon
OL,7,FIn 2019, the Conservative government
OL,8,Fannounced plans to introduce higher
OL,9,Ffines for drivers who idle, but this
OL,10,Fnever took place.
OL,12,FLord Chris Grayling, then-transport
OL,13,Fsecretary, said at the time that
OL,14,Fcombating idling would be "an easy way
OL,15,Fto drive down dangerously high levels
OL,16,Fof pollution".
